<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF109-732-861  </DOCNO><DOCID>09 732 861.andO;</DOCID><JOURNAL>InfoWorld  Dec 24 1990 v12 n52 p31(8).andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Combing the stacks. (Software Review) (evaluation and comparisonof Ask Sam, Folio Views, Lotus Magellan and Zyindex text retrievalpackages) (evaluation)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Marshall, Patrick; Chapin, Rod; Lyons, Patrick.andM;</AUTHOR><TEXT><ABSTRACT>An evaluation, benchmarking and comparison of four text retrievalsoftware packages concludes that Zylab Corp's (Buffalo Grove, IL)$295 Zyindex 3.0 and Folio Corp's $495 Folio Views 2.0 are theoutstanding choices.andP;  The other two packages reviewed are Ask SamSystems' (Perry, FL) $295 Ask Sam 4.2 and Lotus Development Corp's(Cambridge, MA) $139 Lotus Magellan 2.0.andP;  The programs areparticularly designed for the searching of large volumes of textand data for text strings while retaining the target documents'formatting.andP;  Other capabilities may include indexing of strings,archiving, linking of records to create electronic documents andsorting.andP;  Folio Views features high flexibility, hypertextlinking, compatibility with multiple file formats and powerfulsearch capabilities.andP;  The easy-to-use Zyindex features powerfulsearch capabilities and excellent documentation.andM;</ABSTRACT></TEXT><DESCRIPT>Company:   askSam Systems Inc. (Products)Folio Corp. (Products)Lotus Development Corp. (Products)Zylab Corp. (Products).andO;Ticker:    LOTS.andO;Product:   askSam 4.2 (Data base management system)Folio Views 2.0 (Data base management system)Lotus Magellan 2.0 (Data base management system)Zyindex 3.0 (Data base management system).andO;Topic:     Text Data BasesSearchingSoftware PackagesEvaluationSpecifications.andO;Feature:   illustrationtablechart.andO;Caption:   Performance of packages on nine benchmarks. (table)Report card: text retrieval software. (table)Product summaries. (chart)andM;</DESCRIPT></DOC>